{
  "stem": "27748.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened then, he set up shop with no experience, really not having the support structure for running a business.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so that showed up in business practices that were not the best.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in my particular case, for instance, I got the job through some government employment agency, where they said they would pay you so much a week.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was $20 a week, or 30, something in that range.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I found that at the end of the first week that this included working overtime on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What they said was the regular weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I complained about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they made a big scene, saying, well, we'll raise your salary, and made it the legal amount.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then some weeks later, they fired me, because I was a troublemaker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so the long and the short of it is that this kind of Jewish enterprise existed on the margin of respectability, partly because of the discrimination against Jews in that field.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so you have a self-fulfilling prophecy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I ran into that again in the next job, which was in Dayton, Ohio-- in Cleveland, Ohio, a similar kind of experience.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, anyway, I thought I was getting back into chemistry through getting work in chemical factories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But while living in Cleveland, I lived in a student co-op through-- really, through the initiative of my cousin Ted.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He told me about a student co-op in Cleveland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's go back to New York.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then I heard about a job through about a job in Cleveland, in the same line of work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was, again, a Jewish company, again where I had similar kinds of difficulties.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't want to go into them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
